headline: Why European Wax Center (EWCZ) Stock Is Falling Today
summary: Shares of beauty and waxing service franchise European Wax Center (NASDAQ:EWCZ) fell 3% in the afternoon session after the company announced a shake-up in its executive leadership team, appointing a new Chief Operating Officer and Chief Development Officer. European Wax Center named Angela Jaskolski as its new COO and Kurt Smith as Chief Development Officer.
